# Type: feat, fix, docs, style, refactor, test, chore
# Subject: 50 chars max, no period, imperative mood
# Body: 72 chars per line, explain what and why
# Footer: reference issues, breaking changes

# Example:
# feat: Add automated UI testing with Playwright
# 
# - Set up Playwright configuration for desktop and mobile testing
# - Add tests for signup flow, dropdowns, and authentication
# - Integrate UI tests into GitHub Actions CI pipeline
